26:42.293 --> 26:46.278
in a very thin raincoat, and we landed in Seattle, 
Washington. And Lord, I don't know how cold it was,

26:46.799 --> 26:49.622
but that raincoat wasn't enough. But when I got off 
the plane to Dallas and came out, I was one of the

26:50.303 --> 26:56.310
last ones out of the plane. And when I walked out, 
there was this little three-year-old kid that

26:56.330 --> 27:01.757
kept saying, Daddy, Daddy, Daddy, everybody in 
